collectionMetadata.name: Cumulative HDB Properties/Facilities Completed Since 1960
collectionMetadata.description: Data refers to cumulative units of dwelling units and non-residential properties that were completed since 1960.

datasetMetadata.name: Cumulative Industrial Properties Completed Since 1960
datasetMetadata.description:
Ready-built factories include the following: Terrace Workshops, Industrial Shops, Warehouses, Industrial Complexes, Prototype Factories and Canteens/Eating Houses in industrial estates. 

Data on ready-built factories include the Woodlands Park D units (comprising 342 terrace workshops, 218 industrial workshops and 3 canteens) hived off to Jurong Town Corporation in 1995 and includes 1 canteen in Tampines that was demolished in 1996.

datasetMetadata.name: Cumulative HDB, Government or Institutional Facilities Completed Since 1960
datasetMetadata.description:
From 2012, Community Centres/Clubs was renamed as Community Centres (void decks) to better refer to the community centres that are built by HDB which are located in HDB void decks.

Data for Area Offices, Branch Offices and Town Council Offices was revised in 2013 and area offices were taken out as they have been incorporated under commercial properties. Admin offices which are located in Neighbourhood Centres were included instead. Hence, the data from 2013 was renamed to Admin Offices, Branch Offices and Town Council Offices.

datasetMetadata.name: Cumulative Dwelling Units Completed Since 1960
datasetMetadata.description: Data refers to dwelling units constructed by HDB and dwelling units constructed by private developers under the Design, Build and Sell Scheme (DBSS).
